Janmadin ki hardik badhai sita!

meri Priye, sakhi, anje, tejaswini, indumati, janu, anju, ganju, patni ji, anjali ji, meri radha, or meri pyari sita aapko  janmdin ki is pyare janmdin ki badhai ho. meri radha ye pahla birthday he meri sagai ke baad. mujhe intezar bahut tha aaaj ke din ka. Aaj aap 22 saal ke pure ho gaye ho ab aap shadi ke layak ho gaye ho To shadi kar lo meto kahta hu. has kya rahe ho kar lo majak nhi kar raha, thik he. Aap is saal se LLB shuru kar rahe ho iske liye aapko badhai or aap isko man lagakar puri karoge esi meri aasha he. Ab shadi karlo meto kahta hu. chhodo kya rakha isme. or batao meri priya sakhi me kesa lagta hu, ye bhi chhodo bataoge to heni. meri anju jhut kahu to me aapse sneh nhi karta hu nahi aapko pasand karta hu, or sach kahu to pata nhi kya kya karta hu me mujhe khud nhi pata. Subah uthne se lekar sham ko sone tak me aapka khayal aana ye sab faltu chije hone lagi he. Roj rat ko dero tak baat karke time kharab karne ka maja bhi alag hi he. Ye sab chhodo or apne aane vale kimti samay par bhi focas rakhna aap achhe se llb  karo or ek achhi patni, bahu, beti va aatmnirbhar mahila bano. ghar se lekar bahar tak ke sare kaamo me aage badte raho. or sanskriti or dharm ko apni 